student came in asking about census data. His data is by zipcode but census data is by zcta which is mostly the same as the zipcode but not all the time. student wanted to know how to join his dataset to a census dataset. I thought this was straightforward but census bureau and american factfinder are moving websites so this was kind of a mess. In the end decided that to preserve the most data, to get the 11 digit tract numbers and join the two tables together based on that geoid.
